<p>Forterra is probably the leading provider of private, virtual world technology for the corporate, healthcare, government and defense, and education sectors.</p>
<p>Robert is a veteran of the online entertainment world, having held senior management positions at Prodigy, Sony and Viacom before joining Forterra in 2002.</p>
